<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shén zhēn ài nǐ 迦南1057</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài yǒu yī zhǒng ài lǐ, nǐ yǒng yuǎn shì bèi shén téng ài de.
 zài yǒu yī shuāng shǒu zhōng, nǐ yǒng yuǎn shì bèi fú chí de.
 zài yǒu yī shén shèng fú shì zhōng, nǐ yǒng yuǎn shì bèi ēn gāo de.
 zài yǒu yī shuāng cí ài de yǎn jīng lǐ, nǐ yǒng yuǎn shì bèi kěn dìng de.
 yé sū ài nǐ, yǒng yuǎn jì xīn lǐ.
 zǒu guò wàn shuǐ qiān shān, yī zhí yào zǒu xià qù,
 shén zhēn ài nǐ. tā xīn lǐ xǐ yuè nǐ,
 yī shēng yī shì bì yǐn qíng, tā bì péi bàn nǐ.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1057</hymn_number>
</song>